        <mxCell id="v147" value="1. Model = markdown config    No Python class needed  2. Build + Query share    the resolution layer  3. Spark and DuckDB are    symmetric backends  4. Custom Python only    via registered plugins  5. All ABCs have clear    extension points" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Courier New;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=5;fillColor=#E6E6E6;strokeColor=#333333;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1">
